00:28:01,180 --> 00:28:04,540
-pumupunta sa...
-Wow!

675
00:28:04,540 --> 00:28:06,540
Mga non-alcoholic cocktail!

676
00:28:05,940 --> 00:28:07,340
[Mga non-alcoholic cocktail, pangalawang lugar]

677
00:28:08,980 --> 00:28:11,100
Ngayon naka-lock na ang ating nanalo!

678
00:28:11,100 --> 00:28:12,780
Iyon ay...

679
00:28:13,260 --> 00:28:14,340
mga sugpong niluto ng asin!

680
00:28:13,660 --> 00:28:15,100
[Salt-baked prawn, first place]

681
00:28:14,340 --> 00:28:16,660
Oo!

682
00:28:17,340 --> 00:28:19,660
Ang parusa sa mga natalo ay...

683
00:28:19,660 --> 00:28:21,660
kunin ko muna ang mga gamit.

684
00:28:21,660 --> 00:28:23,220
-Hoy.
-Hoy.

685
00:28:23,220 --> 00:28:25,220
Eto na, ang parusa!

686
00:28:25,220 --> 00:28:26,940
limon.

687
00:28:25,580 --> 00:28:27,020
[Lemon]

688
00:28:26,940 --> 00:28:27,820
Anong meron sa lemon?

689
00:28:27,820 --> 00:28:29,460
-Gusto mo ba ng lemon?
-Para ba sa hipon?

690
00:28:29,460 --> 00:28:30,900
Parang ganito.

691
00:28:30,900 --> 00:28:32,380
-Ah.
-Oh.

692
00:28:32,380 --> 00:28:35,100
-Tatlo, dalawa, isa.
-Itaas baba.

693
00:28:37,540 --> 00:28:39,460
-Kong, pisilin mo pa.
-Kong, tara na!

694
00:28:40,740 --> 00:28:43,540
-Hindi naman masama.
-Ito ay hindi na kahila-hilakbot.

695
00:28:43,540 --> 00:28:45,100
Kong, hawak mo pa ulo niya?

696
00:28:45,100 --> 00:28:46,340
Ano sa tingin mo?

697
00:28:46,340 --> 00:28:48,740
-Hindi naman ganoon kaasim diba?
-Hmm, amoy ko. Ang sarap.

698
00:28:50,660 --> 00:28:52,180
Tho, maasim ba para sayo?

699
00:28:52,180 --> 00:28:53,820
Magkaroon ng ilang.

700
00:28:56,300 --> 00:28:58,540
Hahaha.

701
00:28:58,980 --> 00:29:00,860
Hmm, masarap.

702
00:29:01,220 --> 00:29:06,260
-Sige, salamat sa lahat ng nanonood hanggang sa huli.
-Salamat!

703
00:29:06,260 --> 00:29:08,780
Seryoso naming lahat.

704
00:29:08,780 --> 00:29:09,540
Oo.

705
00:29:09,540 --> 00:29:12,340
-Hindi pa namin ito ginawa nang seryoso.
-Talaga.

706
00:29:12,340 --> 00:29:16,460
lease keep supporting our drama "Your Sky!"

707
00:29:15,100 --> 00:29:16,540
[Your Sky]

708
00:29:16,460 --> 00:29:19,620
Hindi namin mapapalampas ang proyektong ito sa isang party.

709
00:29:19,620 --> 00:29:21,180
-Well...
-Kaya nga...

710
00:29:21,180 --> 00:29:22,660
Cheers.

711
00:29:21,500 --> 00:29:22,980
[Cheers]

712
00:29:22,660 --> 00:29:24,220
Ah!

713
00:29:24,220 --> 00:29:26,340
Mukhang disappointed si Pat ngayon lang.

714
00:29:26,860 --> 00:29:32,380
Mag-toast tayo sa "Your Sky!"
